snippet.title: How Habit Stacking Can Change Your Life with Amber Tacy
snippet.description:
On Episode 13 of Transformation Talks, I'm joined by my good friend Amber Tacy, H.B.I.C. of Dancers Who Lift, a global health and wellness platform for professional performers.

In this video, we discuss the concept of "habit stacking" (originally popularized by James Clear), and how it can make initially challenging habits an afterthought on your journey toward better health.
